After a long, hectic day, comfort shouldn’t mean compromise.

Meet LAVANAH — crafted in organic cotton by Chola by Sanjay & Shammy, it’s the reset your body didn’t know it needed. 🌸 Light, breathable, and tailored to perfection, this piece blends quiet luxury with everyday ease.

More than just loungewear, it’s your go-to for brunches, work days, and travel. Minimal effort, maximum style — because true fashion whispers, never shouts. ✨

At Chola, we design for real women and real moments — from ethnic grace to western edge, festive dazzle to off-duty essentials. Every silhouette tells a story of elegance, versatility, and comfort.

Explore the world of Chola — where every day is a reason to feel beautiful. 🌷
